<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="68">Material.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="68">-ETHIOPIA: Wouramboulchi, near Djem Djem, ca. 3000 m Arusi/Bale Prov. Shashamene-Goba road, 2610 m short turf/bush heath. Chillalo, moorland 3000 m SOUTH SUDAN: Imatong Mts.</paragraph>
